snippet.title: Thamma Official Trailer | Ayushmann, Rashmika, Paresh, Nawazuddin | In Cinemas This Diwali- 21st Oct

Maddock Horror Comedy Universe presents a bloody love story, produced by Dinesh Vijan & Amar Kaushik and directed by Aditya Sarpotdar. In cinemas worldwide on 21st October.

snippet.description:

Contiloe Pictures presents Mahayoddha Rama ‚Äî a next-level 3D animated epic inspired by the timeless Ramayan. Releasing in cinemas nationwide on 17th October 2025, distributed by Cin√©polis India.
 
Produced by: Abhimanyu Singh and Roopali Singh (Contiloe Pictures)
Directed by: Raizada Rohit Jaising Vaid
 
Featuring a stellar voice cast:
 
Kunal Kapoor as Rama
Jimmy Shergill as Lakshman
Mouni Roy as Sita
Gulshan Grover as Raavan
 
This teaser offers a glimpse into grand battles, divine destiny, and the eternal fight between dharma and adharma, brought to life with state-of-the-art animation and spectacular visuals.
 
From the makers of State of Siege ‚Äì 26/11, State of Siege ‚Äì Temple Attack, Taj ‚Äì Divided by Blood, and Taj ‚Äì Reign of Revenge, Contiloe Pictures embarks on a new journey to redefine Indian mythological cinema.

snippet.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
snippet.description:
New game drops! Developers! More!

Minecraft LIVE is our own super special show that gives you the inside info on everything happening in the world of Minecraft! 

We‚Äôre updating vanilla Minecraft with multiple game drops per year, so we now host two of these shows to cover all the new features. Every episode includes fresh info from our developers, the inside scoop on unannounced upcoming game drops, and more! 

After the broadcast, stay tuned in for the Deep Dig After Show where our developers and guests show off the new features, often resulting in chaos. Vu Bui will return as host and attempt to keep things running smoothly. Good luck to that guy!

id.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
id.description:
Perilisan game baru! Pengembang! Lainnya!

Minecraft LIVE adalah acara super spesial kami yang memberikan Anda info terkini tentang segala hal yang terjadi di dunia Minecraft! Acara berikutnya akan disiarkan pada tanggal 28 September pukul 00.00 WIB.

Setelah siaran, nantikan After Show Pembahasan Mendalam saat para pengembang dan tamu kami memamerkan fitur-fitur baru, yang sering kali mengakibatkan kekacauan. Vu Bui akan kembali sebagai pembawa acara dan berusaha memastikan semuanya berjalan lancar. Semoga beruntung untuk orang itu!

ms.title: Minecraft LIVE - September 2025
ms.description:
Pelancaran Permainan Baharu Pembangun! Lagi!

Minecraft LIVE merupakan rancangan khas kami yang memberikan anda maklumat terkini dan menarik mengenai semua yang berlaku dalam dunia Minecraft! Siaran berikutnya akan disiarkan pada 28 September, jam 12 pagi MYT.  

Kami mengemas kini permainan Minecraft Vanilla dengan beberapa keluaran setiap tahun, jadi kini kami menganjurkan dua acara khas untuk memperkenalkan semua ciri baharu. Setiap episod menampilkan maklumat terkini daripada pembangun-pembangun kami, pendedahan eksklusif tentang pelancaran permainan yang belum diumumkan, dan banyak lagi! 

Selepas siaran berakhir, nantikan Deep Dig After Show di mana pembangun serta tetamu kami akan memperkenalkan ciri baharu, yang kadangkala membawa kepada suasana kecoh. Vu Bui akan kembali sebagai pengacara dan berusaha memastikan segalanya berjalan lancar. Semoga dia berjaya!

snippet.description:

üìå Match Details:
üèüÔ∏è Venue: Dubai International Cricket Stadium, Dubai

The Financial Express


üèè Format: T20 International ‚Äì Asia Cup Super Four 


üéØ Status: This is a dead rubber match ‚Äî India have already qualified for the final; Sri Lanka are out of contention. 


üë• Probable Playing XIs:

üáÆüá≥ India XI: Abhishek Sharma, Shubman Gill, Tilak Varma, Suryakumar Yadav (c), Sanju Samson (wk), Hardik Pandya, Shivam Dube, Axar Patel, Varun Chakaravarthy, Jasprit Bumrah, Kuldeep Yadav 


üá±üá∞ Sri Lanka XI: Pathum Nissanka, Kusal Mendis (wk), Kusal Perera, Charith Asalanka (c), Dasun Shanaka, Kamindu Mendis, Wanindu Hasaranga, Chamika Karunaratne, Maheesh Theekshana, Dushmantha Chameera, Nuwan Thushara 


üå§Ô∏è Pitch & Weather Outlook:

The Dubai pitch offers pace and bounce, especially early on. Pacers will enjoy trying to exploit any movement. 

As the match progresses, the surface tends to bat better; spin and slower deliveries may find grip in middle overs. 


Forecast: Clear skies, hot conditions (high ~38 ¬∞C) with no rainfall expected. 

Toss chances: Chasing may have advantage due to dew under lights.

India have already secured their spot in the final, so this game can be used to rotate and test bench strength. 

Sri Lanka, eliminated from contention, will try to finish on a high.

snippet.title: LEVEL DEVIL IS A TROLL GAME

snippet.description:
Step into the magic of love that transcends time with Anurag Kulkarni and Sameera Bharadwaj's heart-touching duet, Premalo. This iconic piece from the album Premalo - Court is the epitome of romantic melodious Telugu songs from the 2025s golden era of cinema winging you on an ethereal journey through lofty feelings of affection and warmth. Fall in love once again with the timeless allure of an era that continues to shape and influence the musical landscape today.
